 * Version: 0.8
 * Complete rewrite using jquery
 * Option to try to disable <scripts> in feeds added
 * Option to cache images in feeds added
 * Option to skip confirmation to mark all entries as read added
 * New and improved design
 * Feed-Groups can now be added / removed from the GUI
 * Refresh now also reloads all feeds
 * Option to cache images in feeds locally
 * RSS favicon

